column5: Ive got a website that I want to put up but need a writer that can outline some of the more popular general spots to fish in the gta area. If your interested in writing this for me, please pm me.
Do you want that in writing, TJ?
Hey,, I've done writing for website, my own and others. How long does it have to be?
this may help. http://fishtv.tv/newsite/fishingfun/urbanfishing.html
LOL Roy  PM En Route TJ   Tight Lines All   Paul
I can hear those secretive southern steelheaders "grinding their axes" as we speak...
TJ, you can always hit up Craig Ritchie but big time writers will cost big time.    edited to add: Is that the way you wanted me to post this, Craig?
LOL.....Too funny.
I'd talk to BLY if I were you TJ!
